author: sussman
msg: A regression test for issue #1017.  As expected, this test passes over
ra_local and fails over ra_dav.  (Currently commented out.)
* commit_tests.py (commit_out_of_date_deletions): new test, attempts
to commit the deletion of both an out-of-date file and dir.  it
expects the commits to fail with "out of date" errors.

msg: For issue #689: Move more md5 stuff into the md5 library.

(empty_digest, checksums_match): Moved to the new svn_md5 library
and renamed, see below.

(svn_md5_empty_string_digest, svn_md5_digests_match): Moved here
from from reps-strings.c and renamed, see above.
All callers changed.
